casebody.data:
No. 10-670. Sojourn Care, Inc., dba Sojourn Care of Tulsa, Petitioner v. Kathleen Sebelius, Secretary of Health and Human Services. 562 U.S. 1194, 131 S. Ct. 1016,

178 L. Ed. 2d 855,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 674. January 18, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
